2003;;Uncle Nino;;American;;Robert Shallcross;;Joe Mantegna, Pierrino Mascarino, Anne Archer;;comedy-drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Uncle_Nino;;A father, Robert Micelli (Joe Mantegna),[4] has become a stranger to his family and thinks only of his lawn and job. After decades of no contact, Robert's Uncle Nino flies to America for an unexpected visit, with a suitcase full of homemade Italian wine. Nino helps the family realize the true value of family.